description: Removes a previous import and the associated file stored in an S3 bucket.

parameters.name: importId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the import to delete.

nested_items.name: importId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the deleted import.

nested_items.name: importStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the deletion. When the deletion is complete, the import will no longer be returned by the ListImports operation and calls to the DescribeImport operation with the import identifier will fail.
